{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2501620/extras/CTA_Wishlisht.gif?t=1690906236\" /><br><br><i>Welcome to Kandyland, the sweetest place on earth. Home of the most delicious candy and thrilling rides in the world. It's fun for the whole family!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2501620/extras/SteamPage_GIF_02-Kandyland.gif?t=1690906236\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVE THE PARK</strong></h2><br>As a lone park guest, you return to Kandyland to relive your cherished childhood memories, but instead find yourself trapped in a chilling game of survival. You must outwit the beloved characters that once brought you joy, in order to escape the park. They will do everything they can to ensure that you never want to leave. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2501620/extras/SteamPage_GIF_01-Smiles.gif?t=1690906236\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>UNCOVER SECRETS</strong></h2><br>Using special contraptions that you'll find along the way, uncover the mysteries and secrets that the park has to offer. Each character presents special abilities to keep you trapped within the confines of Kandyland. Stay vigilant and solve puzzles in order to escape the park before it\u2019s too late\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2501620/extras/SteamPage_GIF_03-Smiles.gif?t=1690906236\" /><br><br><strong>Wishlist now to stay up to date on the latest news and updates!</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2501620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1690906236","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2501620/page.bg.jpg?t=1690906236","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2